{"type":null,"faqId":21015,"title":"天气时钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.072916664in;margin-left:0.072916664in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在桌面预置的Widget（桌面小工具）中已经包含天气时钟，点击小工具，可以打开天气时钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>左右滑动可以查看不同城市的天气状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>刷新：按住屏幕下拉，可以刷新数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>城市管理：点击右上角的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70111\" style=\"width:0.6527778in;height:0.74722224in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，可以添加删除城市，也可以设置是否显示当前位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>          点击管理城市界面下方的设置，进入设置界面，可以设置 天气时钟的温度单位和是否显示声音，更新时间等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4678","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837637000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":80,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}